Class AbstractCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.ethz.vizzly.cache.AbstractCache
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MemCache, SqlDbCache

    public abstract class AbstractCache
extends java.lang.Object
    This class defines the interfaces that any cache implementation must follow.
